Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory97.png'}
{3: "As the situation becomes increasingly chaotic, Rosetta's M.I.N.D. is reaching boiling point."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'I only saved you to ease my guilt!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Rosetta', 3: "I didn't think... you would end up getting in my way!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'How foolish of me to be kind...', 4: '1'}
{3: "Rosetta's relentless assault on Lee shows no sign of stopping, until he is on the brink of death..."}
{3: 'Coming to her senses, Rosetta notices the carnage that the Corrupted has wreaked on the Forest Guards and the port residents...'}
{2: 'Nausicaa', 3: 'It... it hurts...'}
{3: 'Evan has never looked at her that way before.'}
{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Everything is my...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'AAAAGGHHH!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'No! Her corruption has reached critical level...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: 'Can you hear me?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Rosetta', 3: "Diana... what's happening to me...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Diana', 3: "You've lost something important, but it's not your fault...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: "We all know what you've been through...", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Diana looks at Nausicaa, who lies on the ground, severely injured, being tended to by Evan. Standing before them...'}
{3: '...are port citizens, their harpoons raised, protecting the two of them.'}
{3: 'Expressions of guilt and shame hang on their face as they avoid making eye contact with Diana.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Diana', 3: 'Residents of New Murmansk...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: 'The Forest Guard has come in your time of need and died for you, not out of duty...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: '...But out of sympathy for all lives.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: 'You have avoided contact with us, averted your gaze from us...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: 'So take a good look at the Forest Guards today. Let our names be known throughout the Arctic Route Union!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: 'We shall be known as the Forest Guard, and nothing else.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'No one argues.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Sympathy... for lives...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Rosetta', 3: "But it's too late...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Diana', 3: 'It was an honor to be your sister and student.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Rosetta forces herself to stand up again as another wave of Corrupted makes landfall on the beach.'}
{3: 'She takes a deep breath and swings her lance—'}
{3: 'The gust from her lance rends the Corrupted to pieces and sends them flying into the ocean depths.'}
{3: 'Her eyes begin to cloud over as remnants of her consciousness cling to a thread.'}
{3: 'Rosetta takes one last look at everyone, then soars into the air...'}
{3: 'Rosetta recalls how she sailed with her grandfather through the dark ocean waves, leaving ARU for the first time, chasing after the Narwhal that had laid waste to the port...'}
{3: 'They pursued the Narwhal from the Arctic to the Antarctic until they encountered Corrupted for the first time at the Derek Strait...'}
{3: 'Until finally, they rescued the Narwhal and, so too, the Narwhal rescued them.'}
{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Grandpa...', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Rosetta recalls carrying her grandfather through the snowy woods for two days, as her grandfather grew thinner by the day from the Punishing Virus...'}
{3: 'Her grandfather was dead by the time she arrived at the port. Surrounded by the residents, she was forced to become a tool for their protection...'}
{2: 'Rosetta', 3: "It's so cold...", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Rosetta falls. As she does, she finds her final resting place by the side of the Narwhal.'}
{3: 'But just as she is about to close her eyes—'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryGanRanNew.prefab', 3: '1'}
{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Ahhhhhhh!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryGanRanNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Suddenly, Rosetta is enveloped in red lightning before crashing onto the ice field in pain.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'α', 3: 'Those who have witnessed the truth about humanity have earned the right to ascend.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Rosetta writhes in pain on the ice.'}
{3: "Lucia's powerful blow disrupts Alpha from connecting with Rosetta."}
